  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>45 Levels</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently 5 maps with each 9 levels makes a total of 45 different levels. Each with its individual challenges. Play on slippery ice or on the high mountains. Try not to fall down! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/7b115c82cb093c7254071c0c5e813cf9.avif?t=1727169142\" width=620 height=153 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3 Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between the relaxed round-based minigolf or the dynamic/extreme mode, where every one plays simultaneously and tries to be the first to hole in the ball, no matter what! Pure Chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/c7c0861fbc567ad0b137f9337c4f4d36.poster.avif?t=1727169142\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/c7c0861fbc567ad0b137f9337c4f4d36.webm?t=1727169142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/c7c0861fbc567ad0b137f9337c4f4d36.mp4?t=1727169142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Up to 8 Players</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play minigolf with up to 8 Players. Invite your friends, regardless of if they are sitting next to you on the couch or if they playing online. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/2eecfcfed8d00be1f076318395f2cf64.avif?t=1727169142\" width=620 height=153 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play with item</strong>s</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you like to tease your friends? Just put a cow on their shooting lane or just start a gun fight. This is as crazy as it sounds. Trick your way into the golf hole by using extra items!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/3e7e1af97d378566250ba13f35775b04.poster.avif?t=1727169142\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/3e7e1af97d378566250ba13f35775b04.webm?t=1727169142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/3e7e1af97d378566250ba13f35775b04.mp4?t=1727169142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Steam Workshop</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own levels in the in-game editor and share them with the world within steam workshop. This will also give you access to many additional levels from the community. Join us now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/903ed590f1fa7459b88799fead117a49.avif?t=1727169142\" width=620 height=132 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>45 Levels</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently 5 maps with each 9 levels makes a total of 45 different levels. Each with its individual challenges. Play on slippery ice or on the high mountains. Try not to fall down! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/7b115c82cb093c7254071c0c5e813cf9.avif?t=1727169142\" width=620 height=153 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3 Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between the relaxed round-based minigolf or the dynamic/extreme mode, where every one plays simultaneously and tries to be the first to hole in the ball, no matter what! Pure Chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/c7c0861fbc567ad0b137f9337c4f4d36.poster.avif?t=1727169142\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/c7c0861fbc567ad0b137f9337c4f4d36.webm?t=1727169142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/c7c0861fbc567ad0b137f9337c4f4d36.mp4?t=1727169142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Up to 8 Players</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play minigolf with up to 8 Players. Invite your friends, regardless of if they are sitting next to you on the couch or if they playing online. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/2eecfcfed8d00be1f076318395f2cf64.avif?t=1727169142\" width=620 height=153 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play with item</strong>s</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you like to tease your friends? Just put a cow on their shooting lane or just start a gun fight. This is as crazy as it sounds. Trick your way into the golf hole by using extra items!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/3e7e1af97d378566250ba13f35775b04.poster.avif?t=1727169142\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/3e7e1af97d378566250ba13f35775b04.webm?t=1727169142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/3e7e1af97d378566250ba13f35775b04.mp4?t=1727169142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Steam Workshop</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own levels in the in-game editor and share them with the world within steam workshop. This will also give you access to many additional levels from the community. Join us now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552940/extras/903ed590f1fa7459b88799fead117a49.avif?t=1727169142\" width=620 height=132 /></span></p>",
